Title: An Act Changing the Name of the Municipality of Montalban, Province of Rizal, to the Municipality of Rodriguez
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 275
An Act Changing the Name of the Municipality of Montalban, Province of Rizal, to the Municipality of Rodriguez
Section 1. The name of the Municipality of Montalban, Province of Rizal, is changed to the Municipality of Rodriguez.
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: November 13, 1982
